  <section class="sect" style="background:#ffffff;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cs-two-col">
        <div>
          <div class="cs-block">
            <span class="cs-eyebrow">Project Overview</span>
            <h2 class="cs-h2">Technology for India&rsquo;s Sickle Cell Eradication Mission</h2>
            <p class="cs-p">Sickle cell anaemia disproportionately affects India&rsquo;s tribal populations. The Government of India launched the National Sickle Cell Anaemia Eradication Mission with a goal of screening all tribal citizens by 2047. Sickle Scan is the digital backbone of this mission &mdash; enabling frontline ASHA workers to screen citizens, record results, and track treatment in some of India&rsquo;s most remote tribal districts.</p>
            <p class="cs-p">The most critical design constraint: the platform had to work in districts with no reliable internet connectivity &mdash; including areas where smartphones have never had a stable data connection. Every feature was designed offline-first.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
