    <div class="container">
      <div class="cs-single-col">
        <div>
          <div class="cs-block scope-v2">
            <div class="scope-v2-intro">
              <span class="scope-v2-eyebrow">Scope of Work</span>
              <h2 class="scope-v2-heading">What We Delivered</h2>
              <p class="scope-v2-lead">The platform was built around six integrated components &mdash; an offline-first mobile application for ASHA workers, a multilingual interface designed for low-literacy users, screening and pedigree tracking modules, and a central programme dashboard for MoTA officers monitoring screening coverage across India&rsquo;s tribal districts.</p>
            </div>
            <ol class="scope-v2-timeline">
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">01.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Offline-First Mobile Application</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Android application engineered to operate entirely without internet connectivity &mdash; local SQLite storage, background sync when connection available, conflict resolution for concurrent field use.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Sickle Scan What we deliver image step1 .png" alt="Offline-first mobile application screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">02.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Multilingual Interface &mdash; 8+ Languages</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Full UI localisation in 8+ Indian languages including Hindi, Odia, Marathi, Chhattisgarhi, and tribal languages &mdash; with simplified iconographic UX designed for low-literacy ASHA workers.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Sickle Scan What we deliver image step2 .png" alt="Multilingual interface screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">03.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Citizen Screening &amp; Registration Module</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Digital screening workflow &mdash; citizen registration, sickle cell test recording, result classification, and automatic referral triggers for positive cases.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Sickle Scan What we deliver image step3 .png" alt="Citizen screening and registration screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">04.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Family Pedigree Tracking</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Genealogical tracking module linking family members&rsquo; screening records &mdash; enabling identification of carrier populations and at-risk family groups for prioritised follow-up.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Sickle Scan What we deliver image step4.png" alt="Family pedigree tracking screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">05.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Central Programme Dashboard</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Web-based dashboard for MoTA programme officers &mdash; real-time screening coverage by district, positive case counts, referral completion rates, and ASHA worker performance.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Sickle Scan What we deliver image step5.png" alt="Central programme dashboard screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">06.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Treatment &amp; Follow-Up Tracking</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Post-diagnosis tracking of patient referrals, treatment initiation, and follow-up appointments &mdash; ensuring no positive case is lost to follow-up.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Sickle Scan What we deliver image step6.png" alt="Treatment and follow-up tracking screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          
          <section class="impact-metrics">
            <h2 class="impact-metrics-heading">Impact Metrics</h2>
            <p class="impact-metrics-lead">Real results from companies that have scaled with our dedicated mobile development teams.</p>
            <div class="impact-metrics-grid">
              <article class="impact-metric-card">
                <div class="impact-metric-num">8<span class="impact-metric-pct">+</span></div>
